---
description: Keep CCOS changes based on the latest GitHub main
alwaysApply: true
---

CCOS is edited by multiple teammates and AI coding agents at the same time. Treat `main` as constantly moving.

Before committing, pushing, or preparing any change for main:

1. `git fetch origin`
2. Rebase/replay your work on top of latest `origin/main`
3. Run `npm run guard:main`
4. Never force-push to `main`
5. Never revert unrelated teammate changes

If the guard fails, stop and update from `origin/main` before continuing.
